    "The polyp datasets have several limitations, including the fact that they are small and have a texture or appearance that is like that of the skin.",
    "This makes it difficult to identify the exact location of the polyp in the region.",
    "According to existing research, most of the models proposed for polyp segmentation have been applied only to single image datasets, however, there may be potential for applying their proposed models to multiple image datasets.",
    "This may result in the tun- ing of models for all types of datasets.",
    "The researchers may be able to generate a polyp dataset where classification or machine learning models have been applied since classification on polyp detection has not yet been explored."
